text-context: NFL Sunday Ticket is a service offered by Google LLC that allows users to watch NFL games on YouTube. It is available in 2023 and is subject to the terms and privacy policy of Google LLC. It is also subject to YouTube's terms of use and any applicable laws

Spotify is a free music and podcast streaming app with millions of songs, albums, and original podcasts. It also offers audiobooks, so users can enjoy thousands of stories. It has a variety of features such as creating and sharing music playlists, discovering new music, and listening to popular and exclusive podcasts. It also has a Premium subscription option which allows users to download and listen offline, and access ad-free music. It is available on all devices and has a variety of genres and artists to choose from.
